ref : https://thebigmansworld.com/hunan-beef/

600g steak
    mariné dans 
piments antillais

soy sauce : 2.4g salt per tbsp
nuoc mam : 3.9g salt per tbsp
purée piment : 2,85 salt per tbsp
sauce huitre : 1,5 salt per tbsp
    3,75g carbs per tbsp

marinade 30 min before cooking
1 tbsp white wine vinegar
    or jalapeno juice
1 tbsp sauce soja
    1.5
1 tablespoon sesame oil

2 tbsp sauce huitre
1 tbsp purée piment
1 gros oignon coupé grossierement
2 gloves garlic
2 piments rouges antillais + remove seeds
    use paper to touch them
3 piments verts marocains
2 poivrons any colors (250g)
    in enough graisse de canard

300g brocolli or one fresh broccoli head

1 tbsp flour

125ml fond veau (1g salt)
    11.65g salt total
    

